# Local skill placeholders

This directory is only an example for private profile layouts.

Do not commit real personal or company-local skill contents to the shared repo.
Keep them in one of these places instead:

- `~/.claude/skills`
- `~/.agents/skills`
- `profiles/local/<name>/skills` if the directory is ignored and private
- a separate private repository or private plugin

If you need to use shared skills and local skills together, choose the merge/link/copy strategy manually after checking `make doctor`.
